Uses of Package
org.purl.co.interfaces

Packages that use org.purl.co.interfaces
org.purl.co.classes   
org.purl.co.interfaces   
 

Classes in org.purl.co.interfaces used by org.purl.co.classes
COBag
          This interface represents a CO bag, i.e., a CO collection without order but with repetition.
COCollection
          This interface represents a CO collection, i.e., either a CO set, bag or list.
COEnvironment
          This interface represents a container for CO collection.
COItem
          This interface represents a CO item, that is a particular object used in the CO ontology for allowing repetition of elements within a bag or list.
COList
          This interface represents a CO list as a specialisation of a CO bag, i.e., a CO collection with order and repetition.
COListItem
          This interface represents a CO list item, that is a particular CO item used in the CO ontology for allowing order and repetition of elements within a list.
COSet
          This interface represents a CO set, i.e., a CO collection without order and repetition.
